      "content": "thanks for listening. but sometimes i wonder if there's actually any point to trying to move past it. like, what if this is just what life is now? just this endless weight? i feel like i'm just dragging myself through the days for no reason at all. it would be such a relief to just finally let go of it all and not have to fight this every single second.",
